Text: Was wondering what might've happened to last week's Minutemen pack. Good to see you have a home here!

Thanks to the scanners and uploader.

Note: The double page spread, pages 18-19, of "Sub-Mariner 06 (of 06) (2008) (Minutemen-DarthScanner)" is badly scanned, with misaligned borders and only part of page 18 visible.
